title: 820-3476 a1502 no green/orange light on magsafe charger
message:
hello everyone i have a1502 cant charge on normal charger totally no light i change already the charging port but when im using my psu with by-3200 cable it works fine
btw i changed the :
u7100
d7105
q7010
d7005 all these came from working board but same problem
hope somebody can help me
thanks in advance...

title: 820-3476 a1502 no green/orange light on magsafe charger
message:
Original charger is smart enough to detect leakage and gets blocked.
Usually Q7180, or D7010.

title: 820-3476 a1502 no green/orange light on magsafe charger
message:

[/QUOTE]
problem solved by replacing q7180
